## Two halves

| | `client/` | `server/` |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Role | Web app (teacher + student UI) | REST API + AI + persistence |
| Stack | React 19 + TS + Vite + Tailwind v4 + shadcn/ui | Express 5 + TS + Mongoose (MongoDB) |
| Deploy | Vercel | Render |
| Deep docs | `client/CLAUDE.md` | `server/CLAUDE.md` |
