## Knowledge graph — use before blind grepping

`graphify-out/` is a prebuilt codebase graph (1231 nodes, 97 communities; may lag recent Tier 1–3 files — rebuild scheduled at launch). **Do not load the whole folder** — query it:

```bash
graphify query "how does the AI feedback flow work end to end"
graphify query "what calls the chat controller"
graphify path "QuestionChoiceView" "chat.controller.ts"
graphify explain "questionAgentContext"
```

Community map: @graphify-out/GRAPH_REPORT.md  
Visual explore: `graphify-out/graph.html`  
Rebuild only after large structural changes: `graphify <path> --update`

**Workflow:** graphify query → open located files → read the matching `CLAUDE.md` → edit.

