## Conventions

- TypeScript everywhere; match the style of the file you're editing.
- AI output language is Thai by default (`AI_OUTPUT_LANGUAGE` server-side). UI copy is mixed English/Thai.
- Secrets in `.env` (git-ignored) per half — never commit or print values.
- Server cold-starts on Render free tier; account for latency in UX, don't assume the server is down.
- Prefer prose and tables over ASCII diagrams in docs.
- When you add or change a non-obvious mechanism, leave a short note in the relevant `CLAUDE.md`.
